        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利全年淨利潤創紀錄 債券部門季度營收暴增逾九成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7aP6ifwhk8Gv_2o2M2tNjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/028e3af4c197c244d1e7abe8c2ea371f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>債券部門銀行家在第四季度實現了93%的營收成長，不僅是華爾街各大行中增幅最大的，也為該項業務創紀錄的一年畫上圓滿句號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周四發布的財報，該行最後三個月的債券承銷收入為7.85億美元，遠超分析師預期的6.35億美元，這使得投資銀行部門的手續費收入總額達到24.1億美元，較去年同期成長47%。摩根士丹利全年盈利額創下歷史紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在執行長Ted Pick的領導下，摩根士丹利一直深耕債務資本市場，在人工智能領域尤為明顯：僅第四季度，該行就安排了數百億美元的債務融資，其中包括為Meta Platforms的Hyperion 數據中心籌集超過 270億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e853ae8b-26e4-3d9e-9ea5-5e707bec9757-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，摩根士丹利備受關注的財富管理業務表現亮眼，淨新增資產達到1223億美元，遠高於預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"視頻： 摩根士丹利債券部門第四季度收入成長93%，為該業務創紀錄的一年畫上圓滿句號。丹妮·伯格報導。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FD5S9s1je1UQ.ue.XhYydw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3582900dbc62e954b759ee81c10bb377\" width=\"950\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:950px\">視頻： 摩根士丹利債券部門第四季度收入成長93%，為該業務創紀錄的一年畫上圓滿句號。丹妮·伯格報導。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至周三，摩根士丹利股價過去12個月內累計上漲了38%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著摩根士丹利和高盛集團相繼公佈財報，美國大型銀行的第四季度財報季正式收官。此前，摩根大通、美國銀行、花旗和富國銀行已於本周早些時候發布結果。在討論這些公司的業績時，高管們輪番回答了關於川普要求銀行將信用卡利率上限設定在10%的相關問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利的股票交易員在今年早些時候接連刷新了史上最佳二季度和三季度紀錄，而在最後三個月中，他們再次斬獲了36.7億美元。總交易收入為54.3億美元，略低於預期。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A3YaXXyATsFUSoxk4vcwrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/67ba1959c7de63faaeac32d271f1317e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除債券承銷外，投銀業務還得益於11.3億美元的併購交易諮詢費。這一數字較去年同期成長45%，遠超分析師此前預期的1.1%的增幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Morgan Stanley Tops Investment-Banking Forecast on Debt Haul (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E6%B7%A8%E5%88%A9%E6%BD%A4%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E6%9A%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90-144801400.html",
